ctive pulmonary disease, or COPD.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039161,0.052586,0.067297,0.079761,0.086861,0.091862,0.093952,0.091695,0.091269,0.09505,0.10464,0.10587],"unified_progress":[0.03945,0.055359,0.069251,0.079287,0.083641,0.089875,0.091286,0.093699,0.095091,0.094807,0.10052,0.10773]},{"section":15,"text":"But wait, there's more.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.11264,0.090241,0.083869,0.075062,0.075858,0.077636,0.080138,0.0893,0.081594,0.056517,0.061881,0.11527],"unified_progress":[0.19808,0.075673,0.061571,0.06312,0.07216,0.072933,0.099225,0.083599,0.082386,0.068376,0.064021,0.058858]},{"section":16,"text":"His family has similar issues, which makes me think about genetic conditions.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.052367,0.070357,0.084049,0.093604,0.096829,0.098274,0.099102,0.097025,0.095191,0.093013,0.074142,0.046045],"unified_progress":[0.056674,0.08641,0.068814,0.094427,0.099616,0.098875,0.09625,0.095587,0.090631,0.084757,0.073431,0.05453]},{"section":17,"text":"Alpha-1 antitrypsin deficiency comes to mind.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020625,0.038098,0.056678,0.075032,0.091491,0.10602,0.11803,0.12017,0.12415,0.12687,0.086099,0.036738],"unified_progress":[0.029665,0.05615,0.084066,0.094096,0.10061,0.11465,0.10695,0.10267,0.096436,0.089266,0.071139,0.054295]},{"section":18,"text":"It's a genetic disorder that causes early-onset emphysema, especially in people who smoke.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.023933,0.033435,0.047675,0.063752,0.082041,0.09964,0.11488,0.12155,0.12996,0.13735,0.098817,0.046975],"unified_progress":[0.032857,0.053999,0.075821,0.092533,0.098884,0.11031,0.10848,0.10555,0.099262,0.093139,0.073504,0.055664]},{"section":19,"text":"And since his family members are also affected, this fits perfectly.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progres